# Local VHS overrides for demo GIF generation (copy to demo-settings.tape)
#
# VHS captures frames via browser screenshots. The capture rate varies by
# machine, causing GIF duration differences. Tune Framerate to match your
# machine's actual capture throughput:
#
#   Framerate too high (e.g. 50) → VHS drops frames → GIF plays too fast
#   Framerate too low  (e.g. 10) → GIF looks choppy
#
# Recommended: start with 25, run `npm run demo:regen`, check duration.
# Only Set commands are allowed here — they are prepended to the main tape.

Set Framerate 25
